Live example at http://www.319.dk/JBID

Database structure:

Field                   Type            Null        Key       Default       Extra

ID                      int(11)         NO          PRI       NULL          auto_increment
mail                    varchar(255)    NO          UNI       NULL	
password                text            NO                    NULL	
salt                    text            NO                    NULL	
ConfirmLink             text            NO                    NULL	
passwordResetLink       text            NO                    NULL	
